/cj.subo8988.com:8988/upload/vod/2019-02-09/201902091549653593.jpg"><span class="fed-list-play fed-hide-xs"></span><span class="fed-list-score fed-font-xii fed-back-green">8.0</span><span class="fed-list-remarks fed-font-xii fed-text-white fed-text-center">HD</span></a></dt><dd class="fed-deta-content fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-col-md10"><h1 class="fed-part-eone fed-font-xvi"><a href="/d/71426/">最佳拍档之寻找爱</a></h1><ul class="fed-part-rows"><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">主演：</span><a href="/s/-%E9%99%88%E5%AD%90%E7%85%9C------------/" target="_blank">陈子煜</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E9%82%A2%E9%91%AB%E9%9A%86------------/" target="_blank">邢鑫隆</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E8%90%A7%E7%90%B3------------/" target="_blank">萧琳</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">导演：</span><a href="/s/-----%E5%A4%A7%E7%BE%BD%E5%AD%90--------/" target="_blank">大羽子</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-----%E5%B1%A0%E5%A4%AB--------/" target="_blank">屠夫</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">分类：</span><a href="/vodtype/7/" target="_blank">喜剧片</a></li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">地区：</span><a href="/s/--%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%86-----------/" target="_blank">大陆</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">年份：</span><a href="/s/-------------2017/" target="_blank">2017</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">更新：</span>2019.07.13</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-hide fed-show-md-block"><div class="fed-part-esan"><span class="fed-text-muted">简介：</span>赛文三年来一直躺在病床上，当医生向赛文的父母下了病危通知书后，他俩凭着对儿子的了解，做了些自以为能满足儿子遗愿的事情，并把赛文将要去世的消息告诉了赛文的两个发小，俊俊和山猪两个发小也凭着自己的一厢情愿帮赛文完成遗愿，结果事与愿违，不仅没达到目的还闯了祸。种种的迹象令赛文起了疑心，当他从山猪的口中得知</div></li></ul></dd><dd class="fed-deta-button fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-part-rows"><a class="fed-deta-play fed-rims-info fed-btns-info fed-btns-green fed-col-xs4" href="/d/71426/">查看详情</a></dd></dl><dl class="fed-deta-info fed-deta-padding fed-line-top fed-margin fed-part-rows fed-part-over"><dt class="fed-deta-images fed-list-info fed-col-xs3"><a class="fed-list-pics fed-lazy fed-part-2by3" href="/d/59079/" data-original="http://pic.iqiyi6123.com/upload/vod/2019-02-08/154959960618.jpg"><span class="fed-list-play fed-hide-xs"></span><span class="fed-list-score fed-font-xii fed-back-green">2.0</span><span class="fed-list-remarks fed-font-xii fed-text-white fed-text-center">BD国粤高清</span></a></dt><dd class="fed-deta-content fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-col-md10"><h1 class="fed-part-eone fed-font-xvi"><a href="/d/59079/">最佳拍档5：兵马俑风云</a></h1><ul class="fed-part-rows"><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">主演：</span><a href="/s/-%E8%AE%B8%E5%86%A0%E6%9D%B0------------/" target="_blank">许冠杰</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E9%BA%A6%E5%98%89------------/" target="_blank">麦嘉</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E5%BC%A0%E5%9B%BD%E8%8D%A3------------/" target="_blank">张国荣</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E5%88%A9%E6%99%BA------------/" target="_blank">利智</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">导演：</span><a href="/s/-----%E5%88%98%E5%AE%B6%E8%89%AF--------/" target="_blank">刘家良</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">分类：</span><a href="/vodtype/11/" target="_blank">剧情片</a></li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">地区：</span><a href="/s/--%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-----------/" target="_blank">香港</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">年份：</span><a href="/s/-------------1989/" target="_blank">1989</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">更新：</span>2019.07.13</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-hide fed-show-md-block"><div class="fed-part-esan"><span class="fed-text-muted">简介：</span>金刚（许冠杰 饰）与光头佬（麦嘉 饰）在一次泰国的任务中不欢而散，自此分道扬镳各奔前程……时间一晃三年，国宝兵马俑与秦皇宝剑在赴港展出的路上被白手套一伙施调包计窃走，自称“新最佳拍档”的飞贼姐弟（利智&amp;张国荣 饰）再由白手套手中夺走宝剑，并高调登报嫁祸于最佳拍档一时间，大陆方面派出的中国蓝波</div></li></ul></dd><dd class="fed-deta-button fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-part-rows"><a class="fed-deta-play fed-rims-info fed-btns-info fed-btns-green fed-col-xs4" href="/d/59079/">查看详情</a></dd></dl><dl class="fed-deta-info fed-deta-padding fed-line-top fed-margin fed-part-rows fed-part-over"><dt class="fed-deta-images fed-list-info fed-col-xs3"><a class="fed-list-pics fed-lazy fed-part-2by3" href="/d/59077/" data-original="http://pic.iqiyi6123.com/upload/vod/2019-02-08/154959960517.jpg"><span class="fed-list-play fed-hide-xs"></span><span class="fed-list-score fed-font-xii fed-back-green">4.0</span><span class="fed-list-remarks fed-font-xii fed-text-white fed-text-center">BD国粤高清</span></a></dt><dd class="fed-deta-content fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-col-md10"><h1 class="fed-part-eone fed-font-xvi"><a href="/d/59077/">最佳拍档4：千里救差婆</a></h1><ul class="fed-part-rows"><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">主演：</span><a href="/s/-%E8%AE%B8%E5%86%A0%E6%9D%B0------------/" target="_blank">许冠杰</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E9%BA%A6%E5%98%89------------/" target="_blank">麦嘉</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E5%BC%A0%E8%89%BE%E5%98%89------------/" target="_blank">张艾嘉</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E5%8F%B6%E5%80%A9%E6%96%87------------/" target="_blank">叶倩文</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">导演：</span><a href="/s/-----%E6%9E%97%E5%B2%AD%E4%B8%9C--------/" target="_blank">林岭东</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">分类：</span><a href="/vodtype/11/" target="_blank">剧情片</a></li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">地区：</span><a href="/s/--%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-----------/" target="_blank">香港</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">年份：</span><a href="/s/-------------1986/" target="_blank">1986</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">更新：</span>2019.07.13</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-hide fed-show-md-block"><div class="fed-part-esan"><span class="fed-text-muted">简介：</span>纽西兰老科学家发明一个名为“天狼星”的三棱镜，它可将人的潜能激发，形成难以置信的超能力但这项发明很快被当地一黑社会组织盯上，他们袭击实验室，杀害老科学家。危急时刻，天狼星被参加实验的青年金刚（许冠杰 饰）和科学家的女儿莎莉（叶倩文 饰）带出纽西兰，来到香港。返港后，金刚寻求侦探光头佬（麦嘉 饰）的帮</div></li></ul></dd><dd class="fed-deta-button fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-part-rows"><a class="fed-deta-play fed-rims-info fed-btns-info fed-btns-green fed-col-xs4" href="/d/59077/">查看详情</a></dd></dl><dl class="fed-deta-info fed-deta-padding fed-line-top fed-margin fed-part-rows fed-part-over"><dt class="fed-deta-images fed-list-info fed-col-xs3"><a class="fed-list-pics fed-lazy fed-part-2by3" href="/d/59073/" data-original="http://pic.iqiyi6123.com/upload/vod/2019-02-08/154959960214.jpg"><span class="fed-list-play fed-hide-xs"></span><span class="fed-list-score fed-font-xii fed-back-green">4.0</span><span class="fed-list-remarks fed-font-xii fed-text-white fed-text-center">BD国粤高清</span></a></dt><dd class="fed-deta-content fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-col-md10"><h1 class="fed-part-eone fed-font-xvi"><a href="/d/59073/">最佳拍档2：大显神通</a></h1><ul class="fed-part-rows"><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">主演：</span><a href="/s/-%E8%AE%B8%E5%86%A0%E6%9D%B0------------/" target="_blank">许冠杰</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E9%BA%A6%E5%98%89------------/" target="_blank">麦嘉</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E5%BC%A0%E8%89%BE%E5%98%89------------/" target="_blank">张艾嘉</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E4%BB%93%E7%94%B0%E4%BF%9D%E6%98%AD------------/" target="_blank">仓田保昭</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">导演：</span><a href="/s/-----%E6%9B%BE%E5%BF%97%E4%BC%9F--------/" target="_blank">曾志伟</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">分类：</span><a href="/vodtype/11/" target="_blank">剧情片</a></li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">地区：</span><a href="/s/--%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-----------/" target="_blank">香港</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">年份：</span><a href="/s/-------------1983/" target="_blank">1983</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">更新：</span>2019.07.13</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-hide fed-show-md-block"><div class="fed-part-esan"><span class="fed-text-muted">简介：</span>金刚（许冠杰 饰）成功降服白手袜之后，白手袜之兄黑手袜受黑手党指派继续交易钻石并向金刚复仇，金刚与黑手袜的高级机器人大战数合终于侥幸胜利，却马上又落入了牛牛、悠悠兄妹犯罪团伙的骗局，卷入银行抢劫案成为嫌犯，金刚逃亡路上将拍档光头神探（麦嘉 饰）与何东诗（张艾嘉 饰）的婚礼搅得一塌糊涂所幸光头神探义字</div></li></ul></dd><dd class="fed-deta-button fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-part-rows"><a class="fed-deta-play fed-rims-info fed-btns-info fed-btns-green fed-col-xs4" href="/d/59073/">查看详情</a></dd></dl><dl class="fed-deta-info fed-deta-padding fed-line-top fed-margin fed-part-rows fed-part-over"><dt class="fed-deta-images fed-list-info fed-col-xs3"><a class="fed-list-pics fed-lazy fed-part-2by3" href="/d/43474/" data-original="http://cj.subo8988.com:8988/upload/vod/2018-11-29/201811291543473286.jpg"><span class="fed-list-play fed-hide-xs"></span><span class="fed-list-score fed-font-xii fed-back-green">9.0</span><span class="fed-list-remarks fed-font-xii fed-text-white fed-text-center">HD</span></a></dt><dd class="fed-deta-content fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-col-md10"><h1 class="fed-part-eone fed-font-xvi"><a href="/d/43474/">最佳拍档</a></h1><ul class="fed-part-rows"><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">主演：</span><a href="/s/-%E8%AE%B8%E5%86%A0%E6%9D%B0------------/" target="_blank">许冠杰</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E9%BA%A6%E5%98%89------------/" target="_blank">麦嘉</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E5%BC%A0%E8%89%BE%E5%98%89------------/" target="_blank">张艾嘉</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E6%9B%B9%E8%BE%BE%E5%8D%8E------------/" target="_blank">曹达华</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E5%88%A9%E6%99%BA------------/" target="_blank">利智</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">导演：</span><a href="/s/-----%E6%9B%BE%E5%BF%97%E4%BC%9F--------/" target="_blank">曾志伟</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-----%E6%9E%97%E5%B2%AD%E4%B8%9C--------/" target="_blank">林岭东</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-----%E5%88%98%E5%AE%B6%E8%89%AF--------/" target="_blank">刘家良</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">分类：</span><a href="/vodtype/6/" target="_blank">动作片</a></li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">地区：</span><a href="/s/--%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-----------/" target="_blank">香港</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">年份：</span><a href="/s/-------------1982/" target="_blank">1982</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">更新：</span>2019.07.13</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-hide fed-show-md-block"><div class="fed-part-esan"><span class="fed-text-muted">简介：</span>电影讲述了神偷黑猫盗宝时无间中遗下一只白手套展开，警方怀疑是国际犯罪集团的“白手套”所为，于是惊动国际刑警，派光头神探前来查案；而黑手党因为有人冒充其“白手套&quot;四处犯罪，也派杀手来港调查这倒让黑猫感到危机重重，为保命向警方自首，并一起对付真正的“白手套”</div></li></ul></dd><dd class="fed-deta-button fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-part-rows"><a class="fed-deta-play fed-rims-info fed-btns-info fed-btns-green fed-col-xs4" href="/d/43474/">查看详情</a></dd></dl><dl class="fed-deta-info fed-deta-padding fed-line-top fed-margin fed-part-rows fed-part-over"><dt class="fed-deta-images fed-list-info fed-col-xs3"><a class="fed-list-pics fed-lazy fed-part-2by3" href="/d/39423/" data-original="http://cj.subo8988.com:8988/upload/vod/2018-11-22/201811221542867459.jpg"><span class="fed-list-play fed-hide-xs"></span><span class="fed-list-score fed-font-xii fed-back-green">9.0</span><span class="fed-list-remarks fed-font-xii fed-text-white fed-text-center">HD</span></a></dt><dd class="fed-deta-content fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-col-md10"><h1 class="fed-part-eone fed-font-xvi"><a href="/d/39423/">最佳拍档3：女皇密令</a></h1><ul class="fed-part-rows"><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">主演：</span><a href="/s/-%E8%AE%B8%E5%86%A0%E6%9D%B0------------/" target="_blank">许冠杰</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E9%BA%A6%E5%98%89------------/" target="_blank">麦嘉</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E5%BC%A0%E8%89%BE%E5%98%89------------/" target="_blank">张艾嘉</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-%E8%AE%B8%E5%86%A0%E8%8B%B1------------/" target="_blank">许冠英</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-col-md6 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">导演：</span><a href="/s/-----%E5%BE%90%E5%85%8B--------/" target="_blank">徐克</a>&nbsp;<a href="/s/-------------/" target="_blank"></a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">分类：</span><a href="/vodtype/6/" target="_blank">动作片</a></li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">地区：</span><a href="/s/--%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-----------/" target="_blank">香港</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">年份：</span><a href="/s/-------------1984/" target="_blank">1984</a>&nbsp;</li><li class="fed-col-xs6 fed-col-md3 fed-part-eone"><span class="fed-text-muted">更新：</span>2019.07.13</li><li class="fed-col-xs12 fed-hide fed-show-md-block"><div class="fed-part-esan"><span class="fed-text-muted">简介：</span>黑猫（许冠杰 饰）身手敏捷，小有名气一次，他在巴黎时忽然遭到不明身份的女杀手袭击，当他和对手一路打斗来到铁塔时，伏击在此的大钢牙和刚帽突然出击。措手不及的黑猫眼看性命不保，纵身跳下了塞纳河。当黑猫醒来的时候，一名自称占士邦的应该特工人员告诉他这是女皇对他的考验，现在他已通过考验，可以正式接受女皇的密</div></li></ul></dd><dd class="fed-deta-button fed-col-xs7 fed-col-sm8 fed-part-rows"><a class="fed-deta-play fed-rims-info fed-btns-info fed-btns-green fed-col-xs4" href="/d/39423/">查看详情</a></dd></dl><script type="text/javascript">if(document.getElementById('fed-now')) document.getElementById('fed-now').innerHTML='1';if(document.getElementById('fed-count')) document.getElementById('fed-count').innerHTML='8';</script></div></div></div><div class="fed-goto-info"><a class="fed-goto-share fed-visible fed-text-center fed-back-whits fed-icon-font fed-icon-fenxiang" href="javascript:;"></a><a class="fed-goto-toper fed-hidden fed-text-center fed-back-whits fed-icon-font fed-icon-top" href="javascript:;"></a></div><script type="text/javascript"> var vfed = { 'path': '/', 'tips': 'BZeaGVpaGVpeXMudG9wPTE1NjcyMzM3MTM=', 'ver': '3.1.5', 'tpl': '/template/vfed/', 'mid': '1', 'aid': '13', 'did': '39423', 'sid': '0', 'nid': '0', 'wap': 'heiheiys.top', 'mob': '0', 'not': '1' }; </script><script src="http://jt.ismicool.cn/ppxystop/js/jquery.js" type="text/javascript" charset="utf-8"></script><script src="http://jt.ismicool.cn/ppxystop/js/global.js" type="text/javascript" charset="utf-8"></script><script type="text/javascript">fed.module.notice();</script><div class="fed-foot-info fed-part-layout fed-back-whits"><div class="fed-part-case"><p class="fed-text-center fed-text-black"></p><p class="fed-text-center fed-text-black"><script type="text/javascript" src="https://js.users.51.la/19887659.js"></script></p><p class="fed-text-center fed-text-black fed-foot-maps fed-font-size"><a class="fed-font-xiv" href="/rss.xml" target="_blank">RSS订阅</a><span class="fed-font-xiv">&nbsp;-&nbsp;</span><a class="fed-font-xiv" href="/rss/baidu.xml" target="_blank">百度蜘蛛</a><span class="fed-font-xiv">&nbsp;-&nbsp;</span><a class="fed-font-xiv" href="/rss/google.xml" target="_blank">谷歌地图</a><span class="fed-font-xiv">&nbsp;-&nbsp;</span><a class="fed-font-xiv" href="/rss/sm.xml" target="_blank">神马爬虫</a><span class="fed-font-xiv fed-hide-xs">&nbsp;-&nbsp;</span><a class="fed-font-xiv fed-hide-xs" href="/rss/sogou.xml" target="_blank">搜狗蜘蛛</a><span class="fed-font-xiv fed-hide-xs">&nbsp;-&nbsp;</span><a class="fed-font-xiv fed-hide-xs" href="/rss/so.xml" target="_blank">奇虎地图</a><span class="fe